  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2741610/extras/b66c52e99b5e33b3e178a8a5dd169df2.poster.avif?t=1758033041\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2741610/extras/b66c52e99b5e33b3e178a8a5dd169df2.webm?t=1758033041\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2741610/extras/b66c52e99b5e33b3e178a8a5dd169df2.mp4?t=1758033041\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Features</u></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Levels</strong>: A collection of <i>48 handcrafted levels</i> built to test your parkour skills </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Parkour:</strong> Fluid first-person parkour with <i>wall running</i>, <i>wall climbing</i>, <i>vaulting</i>, <i>sliding</i>, <i>jump pads</i>, <i>ziplines</i> and a <i>grappling hook</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Combat:</strong> Simple but satisfying combat where you <i>slice meat statues</i> in half with a <i>katana</i>  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Leaderboards:</strong> <i>Compete globally or with your friends</i> for the fastest runs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Music:</strong> A <i>playlist system</i> that lets you choose the best song for your gameplay</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2741610/extras/11c08644d02e35efd7d282e5aadea0aa.poster.avif?t=1758033041\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2741610/extras/11c08644d02e35efd7d282e5aadea0aa.webm?t=1758033041\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2741610/extras/11c08644d02e35efd7d282e5aadea0aa.mp4?t=1758033041\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Overview</u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BRUTAL KATANA is a short, first-person parkour action game where your goal is to kill meat statues as quickly as possible. The perfect game to play when you want something short, fun, and satisfying.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2741610/extras/fe2f95ace928c353036c49135e4379a8.poster.avif?t=1758033041\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2741610/extras/fe2f95ace928c353036c49135e4379a8.webm?t=1758033041\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2741610/extras/fe2f95ace928c353036c49135e4379a8.mp4?t=1758033041\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2741610/extras/b66c52e99b5e33b3e178a8a5dd169df2.poster.avif?t=1758033041\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2741610/extras/b66c52e99b5e33b3e178a8a5dd169df2.webm?t=1758033041\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2741610/extras/b66c52e99b5e33b3e178a8a5dd169df2.mp4?t=1758033041\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Features</u></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Levels</strong>: A collection of <i>48 handcrafted levels</i> built to test your parkour skills </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Parkour:</strong> Fluid first-person parkour with <i>wall running</i>, <i>wall climbing</i>, <i>vaulting</i>, <i>sliding</i>, <i>jump pads</i>, <i>ziplines</i> and a <i>grappling hook</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Combat:</strong> Simple but satisfying combat where you <i>slice meat statues</i> in half with a <i>katana</i>  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Leaderboards:</strong> <i>Compete globally or with your friends</i> for the fastest runs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Music:</strong> A <i>playlist system</i> that lets you choose the best song for your gameplay</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2741610/extras/11c08644d02e35efd7d282e5aadea0aa.poster.avif?t=1758033041\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2741610/extras/11c08644d02e35efd7d282e5aadea0aa.webm?t=1758033041\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2741610/extras/11c08644d02e35efd7d282e5aadea0aa.mp4?t=1758033041\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Overview</u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BRUTAL KATANA is a short, first-person parkour action game where your goal is to kill meat statues as quickly as possible. The perfect game to play when you want something short, fun, and satisfying.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2741610/extras/fe2f95ace928c353036c49135e4379a8.poster.avif?t=1758033041\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2741610/extras/fe2f95ace928c353036c49135e4379a8.webm?t=1758033041\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2741610/extras/fe2f95ace928c353036c49135e4379a8.mp4?t=1758033041\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
